// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2187 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c1b04254-5433-557d-b009-c1d845b4fcd8

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
